ANS(  radio_cmp($mc3->correct_ans()) );



##############################################################
#
#  Solution
#

Context()->texStrings;

BEGIN_SOLUTION

Taking expectations, since we can assume \( X \sim B(n,p), \)
$BR
$BR
\( E(\hat{p}) = \frac{E(X) + \sqrt{$n}/2}{$n} \)
$BR
$BR
\( = \frac{$n \times p + \sqrt{$n}{2}}{$n} \)
$BR
$BR
\( = p + \frac{1}{2 \times \sqrt{$n}}. \)
$BR
$BR
Hence the bias is \( 1/(2 \times $sqn). \)

END_SOLUTION


